                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-359-off1993 t18270913-359-cd1994"></join>, 1 bag, value 1d.; 2 tobacco-boxes, value 1s. 6d.; 1 snuff-box, value 6d.; 1 knife, value 2s.; 2 hooks, value 1s.; 1 key-ring, value 6d.; 4 keys, value 1s.; 2 handkerchiefs, value 8s.; 2 half-crowns, 1 sixpence, 3 pence, and 3 halfpence, the property of 
